Mauritius’s Current-Account Deficit Widens in Second Quarter, Bank Says

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-09-13T11:23:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-13/mauritius-s-current-account-deficit-widens-in-second-quarter-bank-says.html
Mauritius’s current account deficit
widened to 8.54 billion rupees in the second quarter compared
with 7.67 billion rupees a year earlier, the Port Louis-based
Bank of Mauritius said in a statement on its website today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
